delete.prompt-message:
Are you sure you want to delete your data? This will:
- Delete your Sky profile
- Delete your catalogue
- Delete your hearts
  - Your user id in heart histories for others will be anonymised
- Delete your maximum streak in the guessing game
- Remove giveaway data
delete.error-message:
There was an issue deleting your user data. Don't worry, this incident is being tracked and has been converted into a manual data deletion request (as opposed to an automatic one). Your data will be deleted within 30 days.

If you want, you may join the [support server]({{url}}) and request to see the status of your data deletion request.

about.description:
### Description

Welcome to the lovely Discord application for [Sky: Children of the Light]({{url}} "thatskygame")!

So you'd like to know about me, huh? Well, I like long walks across the Sanctuary Islands. Oh, and don't forget about gliding all over the Starlight Desert. Also... JELLYFISH!

Check out these useful links:
about.sponsor:
### Sponsoring

Want to give support? There are ways you can do that! Thank you in advance!
- [Patreon]({{patreonURL}})
- [Ko-fi]({{koFiURL}})
- [GitHub]({{githubSponsorsURL}})
about.issues-feedback:
### Reporting issues & giving feedback

You may join the [support server]({{supportServerInviteURL}}) to do this.

You may also use the buttons below to do this without joining the server, if that's more your style.
about.feedback-modal-title: Enter a suitable title for your feedback.
about.feedback-modal-description-placeholder:
It would be cool to...
I wish we could...
about.issue-modal-title: Enter a suitable title for your issue.
about.issue-modal-description-placeholder:
Every time I try to...
Nothing happens when...
about.issue-submission: Thank you for reporting your issue! {{emoji}}
